<body>
    <h1>T3 - Requirement Analysis Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"c0107b975048" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-=
1.Introduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"182db762071b" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.1Purpo=
se">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"62faeae38c6e">The purpose of this document is to describe th=
e requirement analysis for Task 3: Automate Deployment and MySQL Backup to =
S3 for a 2-tier application (Node.js + MySQL).</p>
<p local-id=3D"473afef2b578">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"42790b3e-7e4e-4fd1-98f5-b248d3d618a7">
<li local-id=3D"672aee78-32ea-4e3f-b08a-15cf17557584">
<p local-id=3D"bc3665f56bbe">CTO</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2ea90378-3d11-4a9a-ad39-f2a118b85bb1">
<p local-id=3D"4c8eb2cf4f1e">Developers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"059c7996-5467-411e-908a-c8dd04b0ae8a">
<p local-id=3D"46773f002f97">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94466763-8ae8-4e3b-9617-01795e86177f">
<p local-id=3D"9be9a8c2fbb4">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"efdd8196-2bd8-41b0-a2b9-766a1023e946">
<p local-id=3D"5f9b821eb9c0">Project Stakeholders</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3eeef8838a4c">It explains what needs to be implemented, why =
it is required, and how the solution will meet the requirement.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"786054ec-21f6-4cb7-85b5-e252b3519376">
<h2 local-id=3D"093282758dae" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.2Scope=
">1.2 Scope</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"6d16aade0597" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Included=
inScope:">Included in Scope:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"744373cb-6d71-402b-9946-5a00bcbfe12a">
<li local-id=3D"022b31d2-db04-4cc2-8a16-74ca629bf396">
<p local-id=3D"92443ade0b8e">Deployment automation using a shell script (de=
ploy.sh)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1752ae26-1915-4fec-9bba-240419a22abd">
<p local-id=3D"df5646260871">MySQL backup automation using a shell script (=
db_backup.sh)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"24825db7-635b-4c9d-a028-8e43f049fe78">
<p local-id=3D"45a747b30985">S3 storage for database backups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67d47987-c44b-4957-b654-96cb6d48dbb3">
<p local-id=3D"54e240de60bc">Cron job scheduling (every 1 hour)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"246fbb49-2ba0-4197-97cb-7ff2234180c4">
<p local-id=3D"7c3bc93a3efb">Two EC2 instance architecture:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"64cdcc61-abef-485e-bbac-e0085af69972">
<li local-id=3D"068736a1-9780-4f7d-8756-6b3e3ec528e2">
<p local-id=3D"2a5a50b46d9f">Application Server (Node.js)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f26e20de-9215-42b1-97ab-a8bb4c8a3d47">
<p local-id=3D"d0a8b8ab0ca1">Database Server (MySQL)</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"7a3107d88774" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-NotInclu=
dedinScope:">Not Included in Scope:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"1ab45ab2-d589-4fd4-b3b0-d186a219c499">
<li local-id=3D"9e6dfd80-513f-4f7c-b5e3-e9f46d200d2a">
<p local-id=3D"8fcf83860edd">CI/CD pipeline integration (Jenkins/GitHub Act=
ions)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"05cb6340-6a43-4e03-87d5-2f25218a28a0">
<p local-id=3D"e93803c72a9d">Load balancing or high availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7167d6be-5e1a-418e-9e1e-04ccd2f865a3">
<p local-id=3D"e0caef56dd77">Infrastructure as Code (Terraform/CloudFormati=
on)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"95f5276f-b93c-4c82-a6bc-70823bda7a9d">
<p local-id=3D"e855e41c3f76">Monitoring tools like CloudWatch dashboards</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3a7247c1-7ab0-49be-8f1a-2ed525768862">
