<hr local-id=3D"888c84c1-4301-4cbe-beef-36782c9bd282">
<h2 local-id=3D"883e7c984a08" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.4Refer=
ences">1.4 References</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"7310ec91-0b38-4550-aefd-5ce7266b7b54">
<li local-id=3D"792cff66-5a16-41d1-8059-660141f51483">
<p local-id=3D"0029ee87c812">GitHub Repository: bezkoder/nodejs-express-mys=
ql</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5cb2254c-af79-404f-aa9a-60ef461623bd">
<p local-id=3D"cadea8661b8f">AWS EC2 Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e8d59455-58e6-4297-b7c9-dbee525ef487">
<p local-id=3D"4c2b1e369643">AWS S3 Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"600af236-5137-40b8-839e-6dc089dc3114">
<p local-id=3D"4c837ce6d123">MySQL Documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a9f891a-315d-4911-8c59-b1e796c5b4de">
<p local-id=3D"2ec349bcd927">Task Email shared by IAMOPS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c466b40c-1483-45bc-99f8-6c9ea32c9f2f">
<p local-id=3D"cfb3f46e8e39">Confluence Requirement Link: <a href=3D"https:=
//iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/x/A4BHag" local-id=3D"8057683e52b8" data-card-a=
ppearance=3D"inline" rel=3D"nofollow">https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/x/A=
4BHag</a></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0661c74f-8d1a-49c9-b15e-6911637d5fcf">
<h2 local-id=3D"1bfcb8e0a4e0" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.5Overv=
iew">1.5 Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"5470c94fcebc">This document describes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"65f25213-74e4-49e9-8f6c-23508cba9368">
<li local-id=3D"326de7ef-d78c-42cb-a8cc-468b48b86e39">
<p local-id=3D"dc8d4368dfe3">Project objectives</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f675e48e-ba2a-4134-b790-0eaf8abe388d">
<p local-id=3D"323b22c4330f">Functional requirements (deployment + backup a=
utomation)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44fbf10d-a8a9-4468-8b28-4ecf3130bf05">
<p local-id=3D"16bc524d0e3c">Non-functional requirements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a94f2d1c-feaa-4aad-8906-2b75f680c414">
<p local-id=3D"1aff6c6e10dc">Risks and mitigation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7c170b02-8914-40d0-83a3-3a3e381fb8e8">
<p local-id=3D"5a111a0a9cad">Assumptions and dependencies</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4b63f72c-5bf8-423e-93a6-899c973a9bc4">
<h1 local-id=3D"bc0a05f05b99" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.Projec=
tOverview">2. Project Overview</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"f7c5622f-b6f0-44c5-bb5e-2a7195c9c703">
<h2 local-id=3D"c22216d4c231" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.1Proje=
ctObjectives">2.1 Project Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"1c600156c0d0">The main objectives of this project are:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"3e97b508-53a3-4761-a2ca-99124d638fcd">
<li local-id=3D"8d6539d9-de0f-46ae-ad62-54b77537820e">
<p local-id=3D"228b3c1903da">Automate application deployment process.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"e836d7a4-3656-4156-a88f-fa62c699f331">
<p local-id=3D"2cd2ba111135">Automate MySQL database backups.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0bd6c4f4-aeb6-4d65-afb9-d8b59c593d9d">
<p local-id=3D"9398a432ae13">Store backups securely in Amazon S3.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6ddc55e6-a284-49b2-a46b-df0f1551271b">
<p local-id=3D"2d7c8ebf01ab">Schedule backups every 1 hour.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ca3fc3f-0aaa-480c-a176-53761b9c5b8c">
<p local-id=3D"188b426c9807">Ensure separation of application and database =
layers.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"10693cf0-ff06-4c86-9239-ef4b674c2875">
<h2 local-id=3D"fa854dd6a88f" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.2Busin=
essGoals">2.2 Business Goals</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"34936bf3-7bbb-422a-9344-8024a1851f89">
<li local-id=3D"1bff3a83-d803-4a0d-b537-74dde2fabc57">
<p local-id=3D"c9f3daaf2a13">Reduce manual deployment effort.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"157ae46f-c680-4d1a-8865-005adf7e71fe">
<p local-id=3D"d54e2eab0ef1">Prevent data loss by automating backups.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"2bf1c72b-a583-4173-bebd-44281bedf683">
<p local-id=3D"964f29725e6e">Improve operational efficiency.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"99a59850-ce91-4e74-9bb9-794323983a0e">
<p local-id=3D"502f3baa7ed5">Provide basic disaster recovery mechanism.</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"a55d5b05-e3c0-4f54-8b23-905da84e4b00">
<p local-id=3D"95be3ef7d33b">Demonstrate DevOps automation capabilities.</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a16023c7-e653-4080-975e-31f4f7fda750">
<h2 local-id=3D"2c02410d811c" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.3Backg=
round">2.3 Background</h2>
<p local-id=3D"4cf03f168f13">The organization required automation for a 2-t=
ier Node.js and MySQL application.<br>
Currently, deployments and backups were manual.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ea3363f7149b">Manual processes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c3643ecd-6329-4ad6-8cee-defd298fd957">
<li local-id=3D"032c799d-c87c-40b7-994d-044dfdbfd526">
<p local-id=3D"d305b9cf8786">Manual git pull</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19c36859-da63-4206-9bf2-c7578e2414f4">
<p local-id=3D"7a43743d7932">Manual PM2 restart</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3aba7484-624f-4ebf-8c19-a88bfdbe7be3">
<p local-id=3D"6d466b4faa8e">Manual mysqldump</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3f5e3cd2-dc0c-4816-8877-8a8cca9b090a">
<p local-id=3D"ad3502f4cf4d">Manual backup storage</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"db3f7002de4f">To improve reliability and efficiency, automat=
ion was required.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"24ecdb1e-9224-4718-9e70-56ecabae2df7">
<h2 local-id=3D"f8c3d45cad46" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.4Const=
raints">2.4 Constraints</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"fc3f68ab-a929-4025-bcfa-5a7ac6f22d73">
<li local-id=3D"78cd128c-8f09-4c19-8fc2-96551624fbf8">
<p local-id=3D"f32dfe8a5c04">Timeline: 5 hours</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e7ac06ba-e4ba-4d18-93a2-fa9126afc91a">
<p local-id=3D"5f40be203925">Budget: Free tier (t3.micro EC2)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"55696799-9655-4ae5-af41-d547e561b3d7">
<p local-id=3D"02c765de451e">Manual EC2 setup (no Terraform)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2f6373c5-b06c-453c-b1c1-c7b8dac435d2">
<p local-id=3D"9af6d8a27e2b">Basic logging only</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb96b2f5-3046-4a4b-b588-c1bfec037349">
<p local-id=3D"b612e7994404">No advanced CI/CD pipeline</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"cd1c466c-e4d4-465c-b6f2-21e9c3457280">
<h1 local-id=3D"dea445a87fb4" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.Functi=
onalRequirements">3. Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"b217b6d0-03e7-403a-89f6-9316c343ddd4">
<h2 local-id=3D"954d89c2d63a" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.1UseCa=
seDiagram">3.1 Use Case Diagram</h2><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file=
-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260309-182954.pn=
g" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"c0db06530632d41a0865add658f8f762b0=
eefdb3a29ce87a32afd67f25d5c019" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.=
net/wiki/download/attachments/1786052636/image-20260309-182954.png?version=
=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1773080997379&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2=
" data-height=3D"971" data-width=3D"1311" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"=
0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1843953809" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1=
" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-ali=
as=3D"image-20260309-182954.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.=
net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resou=
rce-container-id=3D"1786052636" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"4=
" data-media-id=3D"bc9e3c36-fed0-48a9-81e8-2361ea5560a1" data-media-type=3D=
"file" height=3D"346"></span>
<p local-id=3D"08bfecdbe786"></p>
<p local-id=3D"01bf14589f3d">Actors:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6f0eef9b-b23d-4e02-b8d4-94a3cc8855f6">
<li local-id=3D"d26eacde-3c19-4a17-9cf2-7d8a9b79a3a2">
<p local-id=3D"38df5c55e04b">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"210086af-22b2-4132-b568-dac69709baf7">
<p local-id=3D"f4d166aa2e18">System (Automated Scripts)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"339b7955a6b5">Main Functionalities:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a91dc84d-1701-495a-b46f-4509d8c4a20e">
<li local-id=3D"95291d9b-420b-42ca-9056-f251d342e008">
<p local-id=3D"5da3613a39f7">Deploy Application</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb7a5bed-6ec4-4d60-8570-7b40ef7091c3">
<p local-id=3D"853e21c213b4">Restart Node Service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e193a0ab-202f-4c22-b0c7-3a50d77dda3c">
<p local-id=3D"42c1ac4b50f7">Backup Database</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92a225c3-e432-4a34-bd14-28380cc77481">
<p local-id=3D"7d798818fed6">Upload Backup to S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c5bd218b-6c65-4a72-912a-25c4bd4df760">
<p local-id=3D"7246e9e4ce43">Schedule Backup via Cron</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"290b75b0-01c3-4f95-a37b-e3030943cba2">
<h2 local-id=3D"8d567a7a0d9c" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2UseCa=
ses">3.2 Use Cases</h2>
<hr local-id=3D"238a9411-7b5e-4b7d-a070-c930abb42eeb">
<h3 local-id=3D"2761cfa89615" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.1Use=
Case1:DeployApplication">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Deploy Application</h3>
<p local-id=3D"5fdc5bc7a5ae">Description:<br>
Deploy latest version of application using deploy.sh script.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e724cd473d04">Actors:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3865b48d-2121-4104-ab8d-9274a0cb7846">
<li local-id=3D"4f1ee538-1a1c-43f2-9a67-35e8f8ed054b">
<p local-id=3D"f2629a66fe86">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1ebe439b6363">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fe8e8276-aa21-412b-9fff-ff53112ee1fd">
<li local-id=3D"4c8e43a5-04ba-4844-8cd6-d682208403c4">
<p local-id=3D"4b3514a69466">EC2 instance running</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ebf99a65-92ca-4de2-a507-d0c0468ab682">
<p local-id=3D"a33c9610aecc">Git repository configured</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ab7f70ef-62ae-41be-bca9-6706e2400c66">
<p local-id=3D"6d9ff9a715f9">PM2 installed</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8ff948df3e58">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0994cf40-5a4a-4c74-8131-201643fa6cdc">
<li local-id=3D"8f5c19ad-bd5a-42ea-a471-026336efc021">
<p local-id=3D"5e75cec79496">Latest code deployed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d8492036-4822-44a5-8ba1-eace90fb32f3">
<p local-id=3D"976fee7acd2f">Node.js application restarted</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cdf00d76-07c7-4b00-9b98-7195de89b9ae">
<p local-id=3D"fc9d5131b976">Logs updated</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"664727df5e08">Flow of Events:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"4f1e36fa-6848-4a19-9449-47fab6a6261f">
<li local-id=3D"1a53fcae-f75f-409d-9c40-8c265f4bc505">
<p local-id=3D"a0e49c70c7d7">DevOps Engineer runs deploy.sh</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bb17795e-462f-46a5-a5e5-1a46aba7f763">
<p local-id=3D"7117e705bd24">Script pulls latest code from GitHub</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f328f260-df72-4aa7-8a8b-bb0696acfeca">
<p local-id=3D"a34af8edcbea">Script installs dependencies (npm install)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"c89da137-5e6f-4a76-9d89-c574121e70ef">
<p local-id=3D"c9834dedc971">Script restarts application using PM2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"01b876f4-1065-4ff4-9192-b635e200a148">
<p local-id=3D"24c2f8f1f7c6">Deployment status logged in deploy.log</p></li=
>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"f5145d843e57">Alternative Flows:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0164985f-02a3-4a78-933b-b4f10f288fce">
<li local-id=3D"2bef4135-2e9c-4843-a22d-0ee50485d91b">
<p local-id=3D"059f47fa7e08">Git pull fails =E2=86=92 log failure</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"45e97831-6b35-4ee9-b389-6e962294d97f">
<p local-id=3D"f59dbc0efc1f">PM2 restart fails =E2=86=92 exit with error</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e7f28fc0-b607-49a4-ae02-82a7fbdde829">
<h3 local-id=3D"466a7e13b247" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.2Use=
Case2:DatabaseBackup">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Database Backup</h3>
<p local-id=3D"05948f7bc64c">Description:<br>
Automatically create MySQL backup and upload to S3.</p>
<p local-id=3D"df98c1b1563d">Actors:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d1c34fd8-9ae1-4ffe-ae5d-9022bfecf186">
<li local-id=3D"667ad5aa-5369-4011-9296-2b921e3c456f">
<p local-id=3D"9ed470a3a8ae">Cron Service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"25d2ba3d-de72-4da2-ae07-f983a6894e82">
<p local-id=3D"f7adc1e69a03">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"aab79bd2440c">Preconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ac140c97-f2bf-4ada-bbbe-9b65b96f8fe1">
<li local-id=3D"a9e33c71-9006-429f-adce-8d61738e7281">
<p local-id=3D"b2e456e9e781">MySQL installed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a36296f4-2bc0-4ceb-ac8f-1a28415ed66a">
<p local-id=3D"e65198ffc5a6">AWS CLI configured</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f858d06a-2d10-4018-8a4c-76af6c5bcbd4">
<p local-id=3D"ebf423407f56">S3 bucket created</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f9665332e226">Postconditions:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ac29bedf-bf23-4ad1-a128-0d4ca9b341ea">
<li local-id=3D"61961314-cab3-46d7-8161-8681d0fcf51f">
<p local-id=3D"449b1ef9835f">SQL dump file created</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb6a553a-bd8d-4beb-941a-c13c2d256664">
<p local-id=3D"2d37864faceb">Backup uploaded to S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fc84eafa-b47f-4ef8-bc2e-aba0885f13cf">
<p local-id=3D"ef23f981fe63">Logs updated</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"eea8ba291250">Flow of Events:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"2f9365a3-b045-447b-b654-de6d84fb3cdc">
<li local-id=3D"7dc400d0-10fb-4252-b0b4-9ddb9d12c7af">
<p local-id=3D"af399323fa67">Cron triggers db_backup.sh</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f241d052-2582-4965-974a-5cb93bdbc512">
<p local-id=3D"57467cf9c946">Script generates timestamp</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6419ed94-6fe2-4db8-a9a0-e0641b1a8bd4">
<p local-id=3D"5d62f88a8f2f">mysqldump creates SQL file</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3dc11b08-ea3d-4b89-b802-98909c1916dd">
<p local-id=3D"5f49b2b141ac">File uploaded to S3 bucket</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"277cd938-ab80-474f-a396-d02d65b81a73">
<p local-id=3D"5829613a304b">Log file updated</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"b3adb99e7f0d">Alternative Flows:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b67c2733-7cf6-4ee6-8706-14d11ba2e7a6">
<li local-id=3D"8df2526a-1af0-4983-bb1a-f0c681eb7b3e">
<p local-id=3D"d7fd80ac3b94">mysqldump fails =E2=86=92 log error</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8cc633c-518c-40a0-85cb-ffa21b9068f2">
<p local-id=3D"72bb29e0e4eb">S3 upload fails =E2=86=92 log failure</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"221976ad-f705-4329-9582-c532d45259f1">
<h1 local-id=3D"878a9dc0261f" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.Non-Fu=
nctionalRequirements">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"43439747-5e50-4db2-a78d-e3453174b329">
<h2 local-id=3D"623bb07a2200" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.1Perfo=
rmanceRequirements">4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"14012239-dbf9-4e99-bf8e-acf46d3764a4">
<li local-id=3D"3a99f4f0-4262-4c45-9c15-062613a60beb">
<p local-id=3D"48e51557e2b7">API response time &lt; 2 seconds</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"494b2249-7be8-4535-8f5c-11a3b40ca1d5">
<p local-id=3D"56a00aec4aa9">Backup execution within 1 minute</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e9340e33-b0d3-4266-86ce-7256567000a1">
<p local-id=3D"e5db98613737">EC2 instances t3.micro (low resource usage)</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b157403f-6997-41ba-9cd1-df305d2199b5">
<h2 local-id=3D"fd3b051a50e9" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.2Secur=
ityRequirements">4.2 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"4fcc36a4-1c8a-42a8-9441-31713b9908b1">
<li local-id=3D"86f16722-e22e-423a-830d-febdd474d164">
<p local-id=3D"5fbf3b5db776">MySQL accessible only via private IP</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22b4e67e-897a-43b0-ab0b-02a34b25711d">
<p local-id=3D"a41ed9a1e5e1">Separate EC2 instances</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2d90d939-98e5-414c-b862-914f34e2dd4a">
<p local-id=3D"27298509c591">IAM credentials configured for S3 access</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"15f7e9e5-e055-4eca-bd67-98cae0d24419">
<p local-id=3D"2d065807ae38">No public DB exposure</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"13040785-944f-48a7-9388-8cbd41ca3759">
<h2 local-id=3D"6e5147dd964a" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.3Usabi=
lityRequirements">4.3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"301ce46a-a657-48b7-afa2-e8e48ce7f9e1">
<li local-id=3D"0d123719-75ca-4371-a1fb-ea193305d05c">
<p local-id=3D"3ee6cdcbd205">Scripts must be executable via single command<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8834420a-cb1f-4922-9eb5-e7818c30f1e5">
<p local-id=3D"6272b4399cfa">Logs must be readable and stored in files</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"aa09806a-0f0b-437a-be81-fbbf9968a0cb">
<p local-id=3D"81328488e099">Simple manual execution supported</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"34a76a53-6c85-4375-8034-6c9da2dcb28f">
<h2 local-id=3D"eca4dee1b61b" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.4Relia=
bilityRequirements">4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"e7034a7c-d2e4-425a-8b3a-547c0ddfbd8a">
<li local-id=3D"4fae5b1c-23bf-4799-a169-060db036a03d">
<p local-id=3D"c4db7253c09a">Backups must run every hour</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2f89e702-6154-4ef5-b46c-8fe33b2bcfbd">
<p local-id=3D"12e9d4e69f0c">Logs must confirm successful execution</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"99188dd0-c16f-429f-a5b0-d8244141e8ab">
<p local-id=3D"6bf72ccc2dc4">Multiple backup versions retained in S3</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"30d5b460-f244-4592-bb44-b2b35b4ac232">
<h2 local-id=3D"442c52ccc01e" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.5Compl=
ianceRequirements">4.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"b02cb87a-313e-4cb6-88c3-08fbdc692933">
<li local-id=3D"8e62d136-01d1-4b8b-a80f-7884725f14ce">
<p local-id=3D"c8c196c80c48">Basic data retention in S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"608687b8-56ea-430d-bbca-f91a3cfdc74d">
<p local-id=3D"02d916eeffe6">No sensitive data exposed publicly</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"09320fa7-f673-442e-b3c4-2af1a762e8ba">
<h1 local-id=3D"c1bc73e445f0" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.Assump=
tionsandDependencies">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"6ddb5371-78a6-4c11-a9cf-725f94ebb167">
<h2 local-id=3D"e6e135724645" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.1Assum=
ptions">5.1 Assumptions</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"290401fd-cf2d-4e84-96f8-fd6ee769b582">
<li local-id=3D"14b7aff5-d438-48f7-a0bd-b85d0f39a7ce">
<p local-id=3D"a10db4e43aec">EC2 instances remain running</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"799df563-71a8-41db-a06c-5903fe7ab627">
<p local-id=3D"fa8f46bf73ec">Internet access available for git pull</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"efaac944-e0d3-4f87-8f60-f10d47945506">
<p local-id=3D"e1c09895efe4">AWS CLI credentials correctly configured</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"97305877-2c2b-4b39-abe4-8a74935bff8f">
<p local-id=3D"28eaac92782f">MySQL user has backup privileges</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4a314f0c-4f3d-4737-8129-a5fe6c5f6d0c">
<h2 local-id=3D"31caf56111f2" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.2Depen=
dencies">5.2 Dependencies</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"df318ace-b294-4276-8257-dc4d2c7604d7">
<li local-id=3D"3dfa4986-4579-4ccc-9888-d38e93d14a92">
<p local-id=3D"d5f357dc7247">GitHub repository availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb619cc0-cbad-43ce-a9e9-a100b1788b49">
<p local-id=3D"8d1645bd1bca">AWS S3 availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a91e38d-e0e6-4321-8cdb-8353709e8be7">
<p local-id=3D"592f9e8bd6ac">MySQL service running</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5a9c0bc6-470c-45fc-a13d-9bc13ad5a30d">
<p local-id=3D"874b6d06f359">PM2 installed</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"5fa10082-a537-49d0-baf2-7db44f1a0eec">
<h1 local-id=3D"1175dc81a699" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.RiskAn=
alysis">6. Risk Analysis</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"97f1a3f4-f040-4ea6-8a19-185ef7bb7f0f">
<h2 local-id=3D"c3ded3c8a279" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.1RiskI=
dentification">6.1 Risk Identification</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"e5=
6d75a1-8965-4dee-ab6d-d85c8cbd274c" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"31b6bf2b-a80d-47d7-849c-12ac5fcc8f13">
<th data-local-id=3D"870be070-ea94-4e5a-9757-4ef2269657ee" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ad4b02cae7ef">Risk</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"08aa46fc-e430-4473-9500-f082e79451fb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"59b0406d440c">Impact</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"11504bb2-14dd-4e6a-aa3f-59b0c0286fee">
<td data-local-id=3D"b13b7d00-b37a-4b29-b560-b71a1ee6ab6c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dfe2eff60185">Git pull failure</p></td>
