<hr local-id=3D"aa17afb1-9914-48f6-b421-f57961e8cc4b">
<h2 local-id=3D"405dd466dc9d" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.2RiskM=
itigation">6.2 Risk Mitigation</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"9ff735fc-c507-42e7-81d7-c219eaacbc4d">
<li local-id=3D"5d90cfbb-f455-4b4f-84d3-a24a3476bcda">
<p local-id=3D"93d23c7f46d2">Error logging in both scripts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae43be96-b1e8-429d-ac57-b7af0f3ecba1">
<p local-id=3D"af2d4b6abe80">Timestamp-based backup naming</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb335fed-62f8-42c0-ae8d-870b8d38fb92">
<p local-id=3D"b8140c0854fe">Cron verification using logs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c0305644-6862-4eee-a5a4-e301c4a741d5">
<p local-id=3D"60acc0b18a1a">Separate application and DB servers</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6b4ae18e-f1e6-4be0-b406-e15cf8d133fe">
<h1 local-id=3D"59bce9a8c4c9" id=3D"T3-RequirementAnalysisDocument-7.Glossa=
ry">7. Glossary</h1>
<p local-id=3D"0e3502d2c0ce">Deployment Script =E2=80=93 Shell script that =
automates application update<br>
Backup Script =E2=80=93 Shell script that creates database dump<br>
Cron Job =E2=80=93 Scheduled task in Linux<br>
S3 Bucket =E2=80=93 Cloud storage for backup files</p>
<hr local-id=3D"89ad9fd9-14e2-4d80-8c3d-8a1c937f5860">
